at the end

1. *On* je pravi naučnik. (He is a real scientist.)
2. Ova kuća je prava luksuzna. (This house is truly luxurious.)
3. *Pravo* je vreme da preuzmemo odgovornost. (It is the right time to take responsibility.)
4. Ona pravi pauzu za ručak. (She is taking a lunch break.)
5. *Pravio* je veoma interesantnu priču. (He was making a very interesting story.)